title.en: Girls' Last Tour Official Anthology Comic

altTitles.ja: 少女終末旅行 公式アンソロジーコミック

description.en:
The official anthology comic of Girls' Last Tour, featuring arts and stories from 25 artists.

---
**Volume 1**
**Illustrations**: [Akima](https://mangadex.org/author/0d7c94ef-3b79-491b-81f0-ed41215096eb), aoi_zero, [Mochizuki Kei](https://mangadex.org/author/f978787e-ca6e-492b-b583-af93ad3cb00b), [Yoshimura Yoshi](https://mangadex.org/author/25c4a43f-70f5-40e5-a910-5d5f0bc4caca), [Atto](https://mangadex.org/author/074f389a-7f7c-49d2-aa5c-a140379ba91c)

**Author list**:
1. Hatopopoko
2. zinbei
3. Nannyaka
4. Satuyo
5. Tabayou

**Volume 2**
**Illustrations**: [Amatou](https://mangadex.org/author/000659e0-90be-459b-a070-875563777d77), [Tadano Natsu](https://mangadex.org/author/72e03751-6f20-441b-93cc-6fbdcd0ccb0c), Hokkyoku Mag (北極まぐ), Shimazaki Joze (しまざきジョゼ)

**Author list**:

18. Kokamumo
19. Tsukumizu
